Nr. 2 is a textbook example of a MapReduce. So I would either use their internal one (had I gotten the job ;)) or Hadoop. Creating an application which could be run in a cluster of 12 CPUs would be a breeze and the rest would be simply the logic behind report generation.&lt;br /&gt;
